US.12 View Global Statistics

1. Login with an approved Administrator account.
You can login with the following info:

admin id: A12345

password: 12345

Expected result:
Administrator dashboard loads with the administratorâ€™s name and main navigation menu.

2. Open the Dashboard / Analytics / Global Statistics page in your browser.

Expected result:
A page loads showing a section titled Global Statistics.

Verify that the following statistics are displayed:

Total number of events on the platform

Total number of tickets issued

Total number of registered participants

Participation rate

There should also load a table showing the organizations and their data. 

Expected result:
A table loads showing a section titled All Organizations.

Verify that the following statistics are displayed:

organization ID

organization name

organization members

organization events

organization status


A clear dashboard appears showing the above metrics in tables, cards, or charts.
No fields are blank or showing errors.


3. Log out and attempt to access the Global Statistics URL directly.

Expected result:
System redirects to login page.
Non-admin users cannot view statistics.
